quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,Nyirimpuhwe (Allah)
  55,2,Yigishije (umuntu) Qur’an
  55,3,Yaremye umuntu
  55,4,Amwigisha gusobanura (mu buryo bwumvikana)
  55,5,Izuba n’ukwezi bigendera ku mubare (no kuri gahunda ya Allah)
  55,6,"N’ibyatsi birandaranda ndetse n’ibiti, byose birubama (bikicisha bugufi imbere ya Allah)"
  55,7,N’ikirere yagihanitse hejuru cyane (y’isi) ndetse ashyiraho n’ibipimo (bya buri kintu)
  55,8,Kugira ngo mutarengera mu bipimo (byagenwe)
  55,9,"Bityo, mujye mutanga ibipimo byuzuye kandi ntimukibishe iminzani"
  55,10,N’isi (Allah) yayishyiriyeho ibiremwa
  55,11,Irimo imbuto n’imitende ifite imbuto zitwikiriwe n’ibishishwa
  55,12,Ndetse n’impeke ziri mu bishishwa (byazo); iz’inyamisogwe n’izihumura
  55,13,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,14,(Allah) yaremye umuntu (Adamu) mu itaka ryumye ukomangaho rikirangira nk’ibikoresho bibumbye mu ibumba
  55,15,Anarema amajini mu birimi by’umuriro
  55,16,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,17,(Ni We) Nyagasani w’Uburasirazuba bubiri akaba na Nyagasani w’Uburengerazuba bubiri
  55,18,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,19,Yaretse inyanja ebyiri (ifite amazi y’urubogobogo n’indi y’urwunyunyu) zirahura
  55,20,Hagati yazo hari urubibi zitarenga (ruzitandukanya kugira ngo zitivanga)
  55,21,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,22,Muri zo havamo amasaro arabagirana (Lu-ulu-u) na Marijani
  55,23,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,24,"Kandi (Allah ni We) ufite ububasha ku mato manini agendera mu nyanja, ameze nk’imisozi"
  55,25,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana